Observed stratospheric mean age decrease consistent with circulation acceleration
                    Eric A. Ray 
            ORCID: orcid.org/0000-0001-8727-98491,2, Bianca C. Baier3, Fred L. Moore1,3, Hella Garny4,5, Markus Jesswein 
            ORCID: orcid.org/0000-0001-8966-97871,3, Jianghanyang Li6,7, Eric J. Hintsa1,3, Bradley D. Hall3, Geoff S. Dutton1,3, David Nance1,3, Colm Sweeney3, Sean M. Davis 
